		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Is there a website like <a href="http://www.nesguide.com" class="postlink">http://www.nesguide.com</a>, only with Famicom games? (Either all Famicom games or only the ones that weren't released outside of Japan.)<br /><br />I want to have a quick way to check if any game might be of interest to me without having to load each game into an emulator individually.<br /><br />Important: It has to be a site where you can see screenshots of the game. So, <a href="http://www.famicomworld.com" class="postlink">http://www.famicomworld.com</a> wouldn't help me since it's a text-only list.<br /><br />Best would be that you can see the screenshots in the list view, so that you can scroll through the games without having to click on each one individually. This way I could discard everything that doesn't interest me in an instant.

		

